text: Federico Garza (born 23 December 1964) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
